perf+a11y: PageSpeed 100 hedefi icin optimizasyon turu

Accessibility:
- Slider prev/next butonlarina aria-label (6 dil)
- CardCategory3/5/7: overlay link'lere aria-label
- Renk kontrasti (placeholder, footer, badge'ler, blog eyebrow)
- SectionClientSay dots 44x44 touch target + aria-label
- BecomeProviderModule duplicate link diferansiyasyonu
- NewsletterModule bullet text -800 tonlari

Performance:
- Hero/listing/gallery: local /uploads/ Next optimize, external http(s) unoptimized
- CmsHeroBlock: priority + fetchPriority=high LCP icin
- SlidersBannerCarousel active banner fetchPriority
- next.config optimizePackageImports genisletildi
- optimizeCss env flag (CSS_OPTIMIZE=1)
- productionBrowserSourceMaps=false, compress=true

Best Practices:
- security-headers: upgrade-insecure-requests sadece enforce mode
- CSP'ye Tawk.to domain'leri

- browserslist (chrome>=111 vb) legacy JS polyfill'leri icin
- beasties devDependency
